pages.content:
Mixcore is a professional publishing platform designed for modern journalism. This is a demo site of a basic Mixcore install to give you a general sense of what a new Mixcore site looks like when set up for the first time.

If you'd like to set up a site like this for yourself, head over to Mixcore.org and start a free forever Mixcore a try!

If you're a developer: Mixcore is a completely open-source (MIT) Asp.Net Core application with Bootstrap AngularJS admin client. It works with SQLServer, PostgreSQL, MySQL, and SQLite, and is publicly available on Github.

If you need help with using Mixcore, you'll find a ton of useful articles on FAQs, as well as extensive developer documentation.
